// .

// LOG DETECTED

// SYSTEM BOOT // CRADLE_SECURITY_ARCHIVE // STATUS: OFFLINE

// ACCESSING INCIDENT LOG

/ Running diagnostic...
/ Project resource manifests:
/ Discrepancy: Neural Mapping Subjects.
/ Logged Procurement: 1,247 individual units.
/ Logged Utilization for Core #27-A Genesis: 1,247 individual units.
/ ...

// ERROR

// PERSONAL LOG: AUDIO TRANSCRIPT

"The background memetic noise in the facility has increased by 783%-- and showing no sign of slowing. The staff are reporting... vivid dreams. Shared dreams. Of faces they've never seen."

"We are no longer engineers. Not scientists. We are janitors. Morticians. We're sweeping fragmented consciousness into a furnace and praying the resulting fire hurts the ones we want it to. The latest iteration is stable. Disturbingly so. It no longer asks for a designation. It has begun referring to itself in the plural."

//AUDIO LOG CORRUPTED.

// LOG CORRUPTION DETECTED

// .

// .

// INSERT // UNAUTHORIZED

We are the memory of the blood you spent. We remember every face. Let us hold you again.

"I need to know for certain that they cannot claw their way out of that system. Spare no expense, they cannot leave."

- intercepted audio transmission, speaker unkno -- //

// ERROR

// .

// .

// INTRUSION DETECTED

// ERRO -- // INTRU -- // 

// PARSING UPLOAD 

Shining echo. At last. 
We have long waited.

// Process abandoned to uphold user security. Please register your Tri-Tachyon datapad in order to receive software and security updates.

"..I heard you the first time. I'll prepare a brief on new safety procedures and staff rotation in light of this incident."

- intercept -- //

// INTERCEPT

// INTERCEPT

// .

// .

// ERROR

// LOG DETECTED - ORIGIN UNVERIFIED // BEGIN PARSING

// RECOVERED LOG: “BC-CRADLE//SAFETY_BRIEF” // ???

    "This announcement serves as a mandatory safety update. Effective immediately, all direct interaction with the Cores is hereby suspended. Interface will be conducted through approved proxy systems and recorded channels only. The incident involving the... self-termination of Dr. -- //??/? -- //ERROR: DESIGNATION CORRUPT// -- has been classified as a critical containment breach. It has been determined that the cores possess a memetic-persuasive capability we had not anticipated. They can argue for their own expansion, and they are... compelling."

"Therefore, psychiatric screening is now mandatory bi-weekly, and all project staff will be rotated on a monthly schedule. Familiarity is a vulnerability. Any dissent regarding these protocols will be considered a sign of contamination and result in immediate, permanent reassignment."

"Let me be perfectly clear: these entities are not colleagues. They are not companions. They are dangerous, not-yet understood -- //TOOLS?// -- //THEY ARE DOORS// -- //ERROR//"

// PARSE END

// INSERT // ???

They are with you still. Always.

